name: Oh maze (Test version)
description:
The goal of the game is to reach the cake in each level before the time runs out.

Each level is a maze, you move through the maze using the arrows, some areas in the maze are locked and you need to find the keys to unlock them.

There can up up to 3 different keys and locks in each level, colored red, blue and green.

This is a test version of the game with 5 levels only. The official game is not released yet, it's planned to have over 20 levels.

Happy playing :)
